children.text: The window opening has been framed using only an undersized sill and head trimmer.
is a requirement of Australian Standard, AS 1684 Residential Timber-Framed Construction, clause 6.3.6.6 Window Sill Trimmers that
‘For opening widths greater than 1500mm, the windowsill trimmer size shall be determined from Table 6.3’
‘Lintel trimmers, designed as per windowsill trimmers, shall be provided above windows or doors where the lintel is placed directly under the top plate’ .
The builder must install the correct sized sill and head trimmer into this opening in compliance with this requirement of Australian Standard AS 1684.
